# Components & Conventions — Baterino Romania

## SEO — `<SEO>` component
Every page must include SEO. Import from `../components/SEO`.
```tsx
<SEO
  title="Page Title"                         // appends "| Baterino Romania"
  description="150–160 char description"
  canonical="/path/to/page"
  ogImage="/images/.../hero.jpg"             // defaults to site OG image
  lang={language.code}                       // 'ro' | 'en' | 'zh'
/>
```
`HelmetProvider` is already wrapped at App level.

## i18n — Language Pattern
- `useLanguage()` from `../contexts/LanguageContext` → `{ language, setLanguage }`
- Each page has its own `apps/web/src/i18n/pagename.ts` file
- Export a typed `PageTranslations` type + `getPageTranslations(lang: LangCode)` function
- Supported codes: `'ro' | 'en' | 'zh'`

```ts
// i18n file structure
export type PageTranslations = { heroTitle: string; ... }
const translations: Record<LangCode, PageTranslations> = { ro: {...}, en: {...}, zh: {...} }
export function getPageTranslations(lang: LangCode): PageTranslations {
  return translations[lang] ?? translations.ro
}
```

