### ImageCard
Full-bleed image with gradient overlay and bold label. Used in all "Aplicații Reale" sections.
Label: `text-2xl` mobile → `text-[26px]` desktop.
```tsx
<ImageCard
  src="/images/divizii/page/image.jpg"
  alt="Description"
  label="CARD LABEL"
  className={i >= visibleCount ? 'hidden lg:block' : ''}  // for load-more pagination
/>
```
Load More button text: **"VEZI MAI MULT"** (not "ÎNCARCĂ MAI MULT")

