## Typography Scale (mobile → desktop)
| Element | Mobile | Desktop |
|---|---|---|
| H1 hero | `text-2xl leading-8` | `lg:text-5xl lg:leading-[56px]` |
| H2 section | `text-xl leading-7` | `lg:text-3xl lg:leading-10` |
| H3 / label | `text-lg leading-7` | `lg:text-2xl lg:leading-9` |
| Uppercase label | `text-sm tracking-wider` | `lg:text-lg lg:tracking-normal` |
| Body large | `text-base leading-6` | `lg:text-lg lg:leading-7` |
| Body default | `text-base leading-6` | (unchanged) |
| Font families | `font-['Inter']` headings & UI · `font-['Nunito_Sans']` card labels |

