## Hover Effects on Cards
Product/image cards use `group` pattern:
```tsx
<div className="group ... overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
  <img className="... transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110" />
</div>
```

